The need for speed The Run to row across America.
Revision
Originally a race without a problem turning because of a series of errors stupid people who have nothing to do in a routine morning trip to work.
This meets up to a certain extent the ambition of everyone but it achieves nothing if nobody wants to do something more.
The new party under squad - The Run produced great expectations before his exit.
He promised to take a new direction with the series of race Need for Speed already old and out a kind of game from jouables parties that would not only with points.
We were therefore curious how will be the passages added during which the main hero out of his car and done what he wants.
As it is already in the NFS series, the result is completely different than expected.
These are potentially games arcades race but all gets to the bottom because of some unnecessary mistakes that already exist for several years.
It is not really mistakes, but rather the expression of a laziness incomprehensible from developers.
The adventure begins very well.
You are caught in the adventure whose main hero Jack has problems characters and to resolve them is to participate in illegal races across America.
You sit behind the wheel on the west coast in San Francisco and your mission is the first in New York.
The idea has some interesting points.
The itinerary is divided into ten stages and then in more than 50 races.
This means that each race on another route and stages in different environments which are quite far from each other and are interesting.
The player did not feel that the game he proposes something similar.
Some environments are also cute enough even if the technical level chart is the same type as the previous rounds.
Finally, this is not the end of the world.
But driving through the desert in autumn landscapes or in highly snow-covered mountains is very nice visually.
The tests are more from time to time with a atypical element.
For example, in the desert you find yourself in a sandstorm that you significantly reduced visibility.
Then in the mountains you should pay attention to what an avalanche do not fall over.
In addition to that the different races are well arranged one behind the other.
There is only a small number but it is enough.
There are moments you strive to surpass the number of opponents (as in a classic race) then you will be running against the clock (classic duel with the clock) and then still you expected another duel with an opponent.
From time to time you also the police who enters the game and trying to make the difficult situation.
The novelty are the passages out vehicle.
It is rather an interactive animated when most of the time Jack flees to someone and you must help typing on the right button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
What is surprising is that there is less moments of this type that what you expect (to be concrete there are only three).
The result is good because this will not hinder and, in the context described above, it - in the elements that dot the game.
The pattern is in the tradition of previous games.
This means that currently there is nothing extraordinary but we cannot say that this is negative.
As regards the realistic simulation you have to look elsewhere.
But while we can find better in the competition the pattern goes very well with the type of design races.
So everything is ok.
The problems begin to emerge after a certain time.
Unlike the pattern, that collisions is not yet at the point.
We do not expect this game a distortion complicated and collisions, but when you have not, in a collision with any object, any idea how has your car, this is not completely right.
During tight overruns sometimes you touch each other slightly but otherwise your car in the mad process.
Or is in tatters.
Thanks to the system... this is not really a problem but it really riles you.
The revival is so that when you're phut or you're out in the context the game brings you back to the time of the last point on the route.
But you do just that 5 redémarrages.
When you used the 5 redémarrages you have to start the game since the beginning.
It is therefore more a tool for the case where something is not happening as it is, something on which you can really count.
Sometimes the redémarrages do not help and it must find a solution recalling from memory the piece itinerary.
The big catch of this game is that the same actions are in the same scene.
For example there are some turns that it must pass a certain way if it does not.
Otherwise you meet on a given location of the vehicles "civilians" always in the same configuration that you have come first, fifth, 5 seconds ahead or one minute late.
What angers the situations when you see the move easily between two oncoming cars and when you arrive, you, you must be set aside and circumvent or curb.
That is equal if you go to the - before him because it is "calculated" so that the situation there always comes close to your nose.
Opponents also have other benefits.
For all the time of the game, you arrive in some places, again regardless of the time, and you always have the same opponent ahead in the same place.
It said the most at the end of the game when you drive on a long bridge in the opposite direction.
The adversary must to go before you.
When it happening to you you hiding the view of other vehicles in the opposite direction and you walk in collision a number of times.
One can understand that the purpose of this game is to do something exciting and full of adrenaline, but it is clear that you bored quickly.
And it is a pity because through a model of conduct simple the game is interesting and places with such action that you don't have time to follow everything that happens.
And it is equal if it is because the concept of 50 unique routes, the order of the races is such that there is no chance to get bored or something else.
The original idea is the change of car during races.
You must pay attention to the gasoline pumps on the routes because you can change cars, however, most of the time that you enough.
The cars are divided into three categories.
The sports cars are ideal for the cities, the American gas-guzzlers for highways straight and the super sports cars in exotic clothes on the very techniques for example on the roads in lacet in the mountains.
And the way of challenges, that are races in particular places that you know of adventure, goes very well with the main diet of history.
You get not only the medals but also experience points to which are added to your profile which is common to the challenges and adventure.
When you have reached the highest level of driver, various objects are beginning to unlock:
It connects with the on-line Autolog which among other compares your results with those of other players and provide you other functions in the community.
One of the most difficult to understand is the situation of the last race of the adventure.
You have your car in the subway tunnel (it looks like) where you drive in the dark on the tracks (it is).
Your speedometer tells you between 150 and 200 km / hour (in principle) and behind you is a subway train that sends you the car directly to scrap.
In the drafting we had a discussion for a few days whether someone has really thought during the creation of this game or if the authors we really take for fools.
The technical part of the game is not alloy, but the visual part is generally pleasant and in some cases really great.
What makes is that in more extreme situations, imaging is not the level and in some cases tragic way.
This is especially accidents with a large number of participants when a fluid imaging you there.
The sound is good and the track is the choice.
In order to please the more and more particularly the young people a new soundtrack was created in the style "I mix everything," but we can expect that no one will buy the stake for music.
Need for Speed general impression: The Run is really confused.
If the game had not these stupid mistakes we could say without fear that he is the best production of NFS in recent years.
But this game gives the impression of not be finished.
The amusement is really well but prepare you to ensure that the mistakes gets you in the eye with the force of a reflector.
The Velvet Students in concert with the choirs of Charles University
The festival Festa Academica proposes for the third time festivities that connect the International Day student with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical.
During the festival occur 20 choirs of graduate schools and secondary classes.
The highlight of the festival is formed of two organises concerts on 17 November.
"The university Charles was an important part in this festival.".
"Among the choirs there has the Choir of the Faculty of Pedagogy and humanities, in the Committee of the festival, the rector Vaclav Hampl," said the head of the host team Jakub Calou.
The highlight of the festival is the concert of the Choir of grammar schools and secondary classes with free entry on 17 November to 14 hours on the space to the national technical Library at Dejvice.
At the program shoulders the composition of the well known Czech Karel Ruzicka, Celebration Jazz mass.
In the evening the concert "velvet Students" in the national House Vinohrady during which occur the choirs of graduate schools and that of Charles University.
The Festa Academica aims not only to celebrate with dignity the International Day of students and remember the 22nd anniversary of the Velvet Revolution, but also to present the public a choir music of the highest level and develop the creative cooperation of young people.
The main organiser is the Union of Czech choirs in cooperation with the school Jan Kepler.
Any action is placed under the aegis of Bohuslav Svoboda, Mayor of Prague and Vaclav Hampl, Rector of the Charles University.
The festival takes place from 16 to 20 November Prague and Pardubice.
The programme proposes addition concerts, high-level meetings, a music student stunt and other activities.
The interested will find all the information on the pages of the Internet www.festaacademica.cz. festival
Vicenova, Ambassador to the European Union:
The Czechs are négativistes and Euro-sceptics
"The Lisbon Treaty has radically removed the balance between the institutions"
"I was not expecting a war as hard.".
"This will last 5.6 years before the situation is calm and that all the players are used to their new role," it is Miléna and Vicenova began his presentation at the Faculty of Law the Czech ambassador to the European Union.
When she managed to describe the various EU bodies and their relations so understandable and visible, to the point that a large number of speakers of the Faculty of Law of the University Charles might envy, she showed how she takes her motto "understandable and openly about Europe" very seriously.
Madam Vicenova paid tribute to the work of Herman Van Rompuye, the new permanent President of the European Council.
"From the beginning echoed the criticism that he is bland, that it is a wrong - - leather, he cannot fulfill any mission and I must say it has cut the breath to everyone because it takes its role to perfection.".
"This is a man who knows listen to 27 Member States, communicate with them and has a clear vision of the direction of Europe.".
She said the new post of High Representative for foreign affairs and defence policy in the framework of an answer to the question: "Who is that the European Union?" "At what phone number must - I call?", as an important step towards the uniqueness and greater clarity of the Union policy address to the states, as is China or India.
Nobody wants to ban our syrecky (cheese cooked to that feels very strong)
Madam Vicenova also reported the agenda that has lived, lives and live in a time close to the European Council.
She called the Czech Presidency of two years ago.
The Czech Republic have solved the financial crisis, rising gas crisis or have organized a summit for a Partnership Oriental.
She called the government's fall very negative and has damaged the image of the Czech Republic.
The Czech representation to the EU is currently very busy.
In the words of the Ambassador Madam, "activity has beaten its full" not only for the Presidency, but also for the financial crisis that continues to resolve even now.
It must also approve the new seven-year budget of the Union which becomes very complicated because of the current economic situation.
As it seems that the budget will be thin and economies, which branch will be the priority, which countries will be helped the most, the least, everything is solved in the framework of future negotiations.
Madam the recalled its ambassador slogans with which she arrived in Brussels "For a Europe understandable.".
"I really don't foreign words, abbreviations, jargon that nobody understands.
As the citizen must understand that it is true that in Brussels no gherkins or twisted round, bananas differently large or that nobody has forbidden to make syrecky. ".
She wants to make better use of the environment of the EU and see more Czechs in the European institutions.
A multi-speed Europe we expected
According to the Ambassador the Czechs have the reputation of being the Eurosceptics and people who do things that in their negative aspect that positively.
Moreover it is sorry to see such a small Czech representation in the European institutions.
The fault is due to several factors, such as the timidity of our candidates, their inability to write a letter of motivation and weak support of the Czech Republic.
In addition to the Czech Presidency success she then stressed the strength and the cooperation of the Visegrad group.
"Believe me, when I come to the Poles, the Magyar, the Slovak, this French said to me: 'Hey, what are you doing here - low, that is still the Visegrad group?" and he is not happy at all. ".
According to Mrs Vicenova, in the near future are tough new rules on budgetary policy who expect the member countries.
This is the concept of a two-speed Europe, if not at different speeds, rather than a "new European Federation.".
"We have countries in the euro area and others outside the area."
"We have the Schengen area, we also have the institute of enhanced cooperation.".
First it was said that cooperation between the countries who want and those who do not wish to remain in their corner. "
"There will be a lot of this type and there will be a Europe at two speeds," really expects Madam Vicenova.
From this point of view it was also appreciated the mission of the Czech Republic and Herman Van Rompuye to determine the basis on which all the themes that have an impact on the EU must be discussed between all members of the EU and not just the members of the eurozone.
History of a mark:
The innovative IBM begins the second century of its existence
If someone were to seek the word which expresses the closer the strategy IBM, the closer the "long term".
For a large public IBM is the symbol of the technological revolution, is a firm perceived as very current and however since its creation it has passed 100 years.
The basis of this long-term strategy was thrown by the first head of the firm, the visionary Thomas J. Watson Sr.
He left this slogan that a large number of global problems can be solved if people are willing to consider.
His slogan "PENSE '!" became the footprint around which will develop the life of a giant future (and also the title of the internal magazine that IBM began to edit in 1935).
It was the basis of the culture of the company carefully developed by Watson.
For we thought IBM means a long-term, continuous movements directed towards the future.
IBM has survived hundred years thanks to the fact that she was always faithful to its core values and however has not been afraid of change all around it.
This allowed us during our first century to transform technology, business and society.
We hope that in the second century we will achieve even more, "said the anniversary the current director of the firm Samuel J. Palmisano.
A system well prepared
Watson, in the 1930s, began to look after its employees as Bata Czech Republic - people of IBM were the only among the first U.S. employees have paid holidays, paid by the employer insurance a uniform of employee elegant and a well developed system of rewards for inventors and commercial.
Similarly IBM has a system of relations with the client well developed.
The company was brilliant early in the discovery of talent - as one of the first companies to have abolished all forms of discrimination and thus could have the choice.
The current plan is completely in the spirit of the anti-discrimination strategy because it will be a woman - Virginia Rometty - who should replace Palmisano at the head of IBM.
This works at IBM for 30 years and currently holds the post of Head of Sales, Marketing and Strategy.
IBM in recent years is what we call jamy, the online brainstorming from what is a lot of future strategies and innovations.
It is not surprising that it has a lot of ideas - in the firm nearly 500,000 people who work.
An institution with a good name
It is the internal and external image of the company that provide him a secure position in the areas of business.
"Since the beginning IBM had a concept rather institution that a technological firm Rosabeth Moss Kanter," said, an economics professor at Harvard School of Economics and author of the book on IBM.
"IBM is not a technology firm but a firm that helps solve problems of the world of business using its technology," said George Colony of Forrester Research Consulting firm.
As the firm itself there is a difference between entering the market and create this market.
IBM - or the "Great Blue," as it is familiarly in the United States for his slogan - in 100 years it has grown up to become one of the largest global firms.
This is obviously the most versatile technology firm - it develops software, hardwares, infrastructure, housing, services of Council at the level of the server products until nanotechnology.
She owns numerous patents of all U.S. technology firms and five of its employees have received a Nobel Prize.
Among its findings stands for example the distributor of tickets, the payment card, the financial swap, the bar code or the disk.
IBM found itself this year with 220 billion the second largest technology firm by market capitalization (the first is Apple), when for the first time it exceeded Microsoft in 1996.
Overview ahead
These are not all the innovations and manufactures who have had the preference of the client and the time - IBM for example failed betting on an operational system own OS / 2, the online Prodige service or IBM computer PCjr:
"From the moment where your business is built on the movement in advance you can't émotionellement stay hooked on the past," noted Samuel J. Palmisano.
For that IBM has no problem to build its bases on a flat - forms and when they do not work it is going.
In the difference by example of Microsoft competitor at the base is and remains under the Windows operating system.
A technology perspective
In the income IBM, services, which are trained for a fifth by software and hardwares, have a prominent place.
However in 1990 it was with more than half the height representative of hardware.
From the year 2000 IBM has sold assets to poor performance for 15 billion, over that period it has invested $58 billion in the purchase of technologies prospects.
She continues in investments and even from 2008, when for the first time it has surpassed the new financial crisis.
IBM is negotiating according to the precepts of his first head Thomas J. Watson, who during the economic crisis has also increased its volume of investment.
It now appears that IBM is the current crisis without interference?
The share price IBM grew from 2008 in rocket 120%, net income of the firm continues to grow.
The logo of the firm IBM is to change all but not its values.
We can expect to this flexible giant control other crises.
IBM history: From the slices of cheese until the flights in the cosmos.
The International Business Machines (IBM) was born in New York 100 years ago; it was originally the name of Computing Tabulating Recording Corporation complicated.
She took the name IBM in 1924 - initially it was a mark used by a branch of a firm in Canada and South America.
The basis of the future IBM was the merger of four firms whose history is linked to the ten year 80 of the ninth century.
They had technologies such as the old "pointeuses,"... which was the arrival and the departure of employees.
The architect of the new company was Charles Ranlett Flint that until 1930 chaired the Council of Surveillance of society.
Flint dispatched the head of a rival firm Thomas J. Watson to help lead the company.
The leader was then to shadow the founder of the firm - it is on the ideas of Watson that are up to now the identity and culture of the company.
Watson led the firm until 1952.
IBM, as its name, began with the production of all the machines for business and trade - trancheuses cheeses and meat until the cash registers.
During the first four years in which Watson headed, turnover has multiplied up to 9 million and began the expansion of the firm in all parts of the world.
Watson was irreplaceable if the firm after 40 years of leadership is his son who held the director's chair, Thomas Watson Jr.
Under his leadership IBM began the development of artificial intelligence and developed the first programming language.
In the 1960s people and computers from IBM helped NASA guide flights in the cosmos - on Mercury, Saturn and in 1969 the flight to the moon.
Meanwhile in 1964 IBM developed the first family of computers - the IBM System / 360.
The PC classic that hastened the computer standard of the time with the name of IBM 5150 came on the market in 1981.
Twenty years later IBM sells its manufactures computers to the Chinese company Lenovo, but bought the company of Consulting Pricewaterhouse Coopers and began to handle advice and services with high added value.
The strategy that succeeds in IBM these past three years - is the concept Smarter Planet "a smarter planet.".
His goal is the intelligent use of technology in areas not yet exploited such as transportation and management of cities.
In the area of trade IBM has developed there was little time a platform "Smarter Commerce" trade, which helps to manage the business cycle.
IBM has a strong history on our territory.
She created its branch in Czechoslovakia in 1932 then first countries of Central and Eastern Europe.
Today, in addition to IBM RT, there is also the strategic centre of outsourcing of Brno.
The Central for Central and Eastern Europe headquarters in Prague and there is also the research and development team in the world of speech recognition.
