The most beautiful pools of Europe
A jump in the blue
In Julia Stanek
Pataugeoires ovni, in view of beautiful pools of Budapest: Who trip across Europe can live his miracle blue - and having turned the city or a long walk - may leave rest his legs tired in the bathroom of fizzy water.
A book shows how swimming pool can experience the most well - be.
When Iris Meder would in research trip during the last 18 months, there was a subject which should not miss in his luggage: his swimsuit.
lying on his back in the water, she observed the domes artistically arranged, and swimming against the marbles Putten who expected the other side of the pool and was to admire Art Nouveau meticulously restored these pools converted.
If a covered swimming pool was fun, she noted in her notebook without delay all the details of interest on the type of construction and the history of the building.
