However, it noted, "In my opinion, they should be able to move forward.".
Only this doctrine criticised since its introduction is between them and a verdict.
I have always criticised the Feres doctrine.
The army is decades behind because it does not have the same benefits and means of deterrence posed by the responsibility.
"The odds are heavily against them... but it is important that they are trying," he said.
These things change only when the good have the will to fight.
