Fujimori, 72, is serving a sentence of 25 years in prison for human rights violations committed during his government (1990 - 2000) suffers from various ailments, including cancer - a language for which he was operated on four times and which is under control.
Congressman Alejandro Aguinaga, his personal physician, said that Fujimori Canal N television will be assessed for three days in the National Institute of Néoplasiques diseases to determine the reason for the pain and loss of strength in its members.
Aguinaga said that in his opinion Fujimori would be a candidate for the benefit of the sentence for humanitarian reasons, without doubt, he said that it wants because it feels innocent.
He was operated on four times of language, it has a weight loss of 18 pounds, weight and other diseases, as a gastrite érosive, a cyst of pancreas, kidney, blood pressure and circulation problems in the feet, said the doctor.
Fujimori is serving imprisonment since September 2007 in the National Directorate of Operations police duties.
